  <GeneDef ParentName="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneHivemind_Base" Name="WVC_XenotypesAndGenes_GeneHivemind_Hediffs" Abstract="True">
	<geneClass>WVC_XenotypesAndGenes.Gene_Hivemind_Hediff</geneClass>
	<marketValueFactor>2</marketValueFactor>
	<customEffectDescriptions>
	  <li>&lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;Efficiency&lt;/color&gt; depends on &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;hivemind sync&lt;/color&gt;hronization.</li>
	  <li>The gene's effect appears some time after &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;connecting&lt;/color&gt; with the &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;hivemind&lt;/color&gt;. &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;Disconnecting&lt;/color&gt; will &lt;color=#8a8ae6&gt;reset&lt;/color&gt; the effect with the same delay.</li>
	</customEffectDescriptions>
